[[File:Pinnacle_Keep.jpg|thumb|right|200px|Pinnacle keep and an Imperial patrol.]]
[[Pinnacle Keep]] was the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] detention center of [[Gellefon]]. It was located in a hollowed-out crag far from [[Kig Dannen Spaceport]], and away from prying eyes. [[Governor/Legends|Governor]] [[Schennt]] originally had the facility built to hold captured members of [[Aran Starfire]]'s resistance group, the [[Gellefon Freedom Fighters]], but few of them ever survived to be captured. The center is guarded by 30 [[Stormtrooper/Legends|stormtroopers]], 15 Imperial troopers, 4 [[Gellbeast]]s, and 4 [[Probe droid/Legends|probe droids]].

When [[Deep Ear]] were captured after stealing the [[Death Star II/Legends|Death Star II's]] plans, they were transported to the Pinnacle Keep center. While Schennt thought that this was a high honor, it was in fact a ploy by the [[Emperor/Legends|Emperor]] who knew that the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebels]] would be able to free the [[Bothan/Legends|Bothans]] from the Keep. True to his feelings, rebels led by [[Jade (mercenary)|Jade]] and [[Borsk Fey'lya]] did indeed free the Bothans with the help of the Freedom Fighters.

